## Running Tests

### From Xcode
- Press Cmd+U to run all tests
- Or use Test Navigator (Cmd+6) to run individual tests

### From Command Line
```bash
# Run all UI tests
xcodebuild test \
  -scheme {{projectName}} \
  -destination 'platform=iOS Simulator,name=iPhone 15'

# Run specific test
xcodebuild test \
  -scheme {{projectName}} \
  -destination 'platform=iOS Simulator,name=iPhone 15' \
  -only-testing:{{projectName}}UITests/SampleUITest/testSuccessfulLogin
```

